<section class="lifestyle">
  <div class="container container-narrow">
    <h2 class="section-title text-center">Lifestyle & Culture</h2>
    <p class="lead text-center text-muted">
      A place shaped by its people.
    </p>

    <div class="lifestyle-content">
      <div class="lifestyle-block">
        <h3>International Mix</h3>
        <p>
          Florianopolis draws people from around the world: entrepreneurs escaping
          expensive cities, artists seeking inspiration, families looking for a
          different pace. The local community has a calm, village-like atmosphere
          with strong international presence. You will hear Portuguese, English,
          Spanish, and more.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lifestyle-block">
        <h3>Embodiment Arts</h3>
        <p>
          Dance, music, movement, and a strong conscious community vibe. The region
          is known for its practitioners: yoga teachers, breathwork facilitators,
          contact improvisation dancers, and musicians. The culture here values
          presence over productivity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lifestyle-block">
        <h3>Spiritual Traditions</h3>
        <p>
          Brazil has established, legal spiritual traditions including Santo Daime
          and UDV churches. These are recognized religious practices with deep
          cultural roots. The broader region supports exploration and personal growth
          within legal and respectful frameworks.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lifestyle-block">
        <h3>Quality of Life</h3>
        <p>
          Santa Catarina is often cited among Brazil's lower-violence states, with
          quality of life metrics that compare favorably within the country. The
          Information Packet includes specific data and sources for your due
          diligence. This is positioning, not a guarantee.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lifestyle-block">
        <h3>Seasonal Advantage</h3>
        <p>
          When it is winter in the Northern Hemisphere, it is summer here. December
          through March brings warm weather, long days, and the best surf. Your
          escape from gray winters is a flight away.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cost-of-living">
      <h3 class="text-center">Cost of Living</h3>
      <p class="text-center text-muted" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
        Source: Numbeo
      </p>
      <div class="col-grid">
        <div class="col-card">
          <span class="col-label">Single Person</span>
          <span class="col-value">$597.8</span>
          <span class="col-local">R$3,226.4 monthly, excluding rent</span>
        </div>
        <div class="col-card">
          <span class="col-label">Family of Four</span>
          <span class="col-value">$2,210.2</span>
          <span class="col-local">R$11,928.8 monthly, excluding rent</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="col-translation text-center">
        In Bay Area terms: your monthly burn can be a fraction of SF, while your
        square footage and nature access can be multiples.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
